metadata.description:
Morixels Mega Colab is the first and one of the biggest Collaborations that happen on the FXHash  and also in Morixels Land.

In this Collaboration, 19 artists have designed their artwork as pixel art. Each artist has 5 Artworks in this collection, which have been randomly combined with Borders that I designed (Morteza Yousefi, idea owner and art director)

This combination has got a beautiful effect in a random way, and besides that, it makes this collection very valuable because of the reputation and Ideas of the 20 artists.

The number of Traits in this collection is 5 (137 layers) and it has the ability to make 930,240 NFTs.

To create balance, these NFTs are randomly minted, and this is a chance for everyone to get a rare version. So due to the low price of these NFTs, if the rare version did not belong to you, it is still possible for you to mint the new NFTs.

To Produce this collection, all the layers were designed pixel by pixel, which was time-consuming and difficult. And this greatly increases the value of this collection.

